  <context>
    <background>
      `InvoiceExtractionToolHandler` is the last typed handler — LLM identifies invoice
      structure + line items, deterministic code does the math. Used heavily in vendor
      management, AP automation, expense review playbooks. Tax-inclusive vs exclusive
      and pre/post-tax discount ordering are the gotchas — wrong assumption shifts
      totals by significant margins.
    </background>
